snippet.textDisplay:
@legacyGamingUS I don't want to be overly critical here, but this is the second video of yours I've seen in my feed that reeks of "written by AI" 

I get that writing video scripts yourself can be difficult but you'll never get good at it if you let the moron bots do all the heavy lifting. AI generated content is riddled with inaccuracies that will hurt your viewership when discovered. For example, horace does not "remain airborne for the duration of the fight"

FYI the reason I know this was AI written is because of the constant and repetitive use of certain words and phrases that do not appear in human vernacular very often.

